            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para agrupar el código en la función, lo sangramos con dos espacios. Esta función agrupa dos declaraciones <code>print()</code> relacionadas.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greet_user\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Good morning Anna&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome back&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"20\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option startIndex=\"49\" endIndex=\"54\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>print</code> seguido de <code>print</code>.</p></body></html>"
